{"type": "article", "id": 13258, "title": "First Cabin 胶囊旅馆商务舱", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-10T08:03:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606152634D6ZUu8pLkSJ9Pqfb.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>日本的胶囊旅馆小巧但精致，各种设施应有尽有，而且价格也往往比较可爱。最近，First Cabin 推出了一套“商务舱”胶囊旅馆，房间更为宽敞，装潢也更加精致，除了普通的设施之外，还设有咖啡厅和酒吧等娱乐场所。而价格也十分厚道，大部分在 5000 日元左右，这是<a href=\"http://first-cabin.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">预定地址</a>。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140844wapOnyPC6JLRTj98.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140844VwbnZMXr6idxEv0s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140845ipD7rxXRZl1C58w9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140846IeRs7k3JOY2MWUmo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140846poXjcrE0R1lhzZSb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140847DeTPKBmuGnagfrFw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140847tu0hM4OzBKCdHL3e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}